==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Diligently
<hw>Dil"i*gent*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a diligent manner; not
carelessly; not negligently; with industry or assiduity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Ye <qex>diligently</qex> keep commandments of the Lord your
God.</q> <rj><qau>Deut. vi. 17.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dill</ent>⟦br⟧
